tags.description: One of those weird collection of bollards and barriers that mar several crossings of the railway. Unclear what the purpose is, other than to be obnoxious and illegal under the Equality Act.

tags.fixme: There's a bridleway signed to the west, so I suspect this east/west bit might be legally a bridleway too.

tags.note: site of attenuation pond for RAF Upwood redevelopment
